parameters.name: Cycle
parameters.description:
The cycle to query the 95th percentile bandwidth data. Valid values:

*   day (default)
*   month

parameters.name: DomainName
parameters.description:
The domain name to be queried for acceleration. If the parameter is empty, the data merged from all accelerated domain names will be returned by default.

> Batch domain name queries are not supported.

parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: End time point. The date format follows the ISO8601 representation and uses UTC time, in the format yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ssZ.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: Start time point. The date format follows the ISO8601 representation and uses UTC time, in the format yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ssZ.

parameters.name: TimePoint
parameters.description: The start time point for getting the data. The date format follows the ISO8601 representation and uses UTC time, in the format yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ssZ.
